{"tid":2023194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又一次原告變被告—【18/5 青衣連儂橋藍絲襲擊市民】","createTime":"2020-05-18T23:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T00:16:45.000Z","uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"53fd75b09716dd7a461ae95dab693121934092fb","tid":2023194,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T23:27:25.000Z","msg":"【18/5 青衣連儂橋藍絲襲擊市民】<br />\n<br />\n晚上8時許，青衣連儂橋有一男子在場觀看橋上連儂海報及補救，另一帶黑色帽深藍色衫「藍絲」突然上前襲擊；並從後勒住「恤衫男」頸部，其後有途人喝止，該「帶帽男子」續影相叫囂，更主動報警。<br />\n<br />\n約十多名警員接報到場，向被襲者進行搜查，初時警方以雙方糾紛處理，及後對「恤衫男子」表示會以亂拋垃圾罪名發出定額告票$1500元，後來又指地上紙張可能是糾纏爭執間跌下，並勸告雙方和解。<br />\n<br />\n事件沒有人被捕或票控，而消息指「帶帽男」是早前曾在上水及多處連儂牆「撕紙」人士，當區區議員亦有到場了解。<br />\n<br />\n攝：Alvis<br />\n<br />\n_______________________<br />\n訂閱 Yt 頻道: PSHKmediaofficial<br />\nIG : pshkinc<br />\nTw : OfficalPshk<br />\n<br />\n如果想支持PSHK記者<br />\n歡迎大家以PayPal / 轉數快資助形式捐款畀我哋<br />\nPaypal link : paypal .me/pshk100<br />\n轉數快：9992611<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/111587046907016/posts/289591822439870/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F111587046907016%2Fposts%2F289591822439870%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F84e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=d8052945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/111587046907016/posts/289591822439870/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"de5abb67d1994b7e414e6166da78b98c1b7a6c84","tid":2023194,"uid":34075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T23:29:02.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac68b5d371e294d9b2b468559a4ffbcae2619d4","tid":2023194,"uid":122915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T23:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aea3053c2c9f3e856970a1370148019715347b11","tid":2023194,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T23:31:31.000Z","msg":"「帶帽男子」續影相叫囂，更主動報警<br />\n<br />\n藍絲同黑警一早夾埋 但佢地原本預有人還拖可以拉返去 點知係藍絲單方面打人"},{"pid":"7a65e35f055f30752800da60f660721f68054868","tid":2023194,"uid":48006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T23:55:16.000Z","msg":"和佢老母個解 同藍絲有不共戴天既仇"},{"pid":"ba3dceacaf730bc44467d77363cfbf0a8c40dfca","tid":2023194,"uid":178800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T00:14:05.000Z","msg":"藍屍點解咁猖狂肆無忌憚<br />\n因為做野無乜後果同代價囉<br />\n13拳肥閪判幾個月=&gt;可接受<br />\n之前連儂另一單嚴重傷人=&gt;3年左右,可接受既代價<br />\n而家有黑警護航更加唔洗被起訴<br />\n的士狗車斷女手足對腳,50萬<br />\n只有令佢地承受接受唔到既代價,先至會令佢地驚唔敢<br />\n而再高舉愛同和平,佢地會一刀插死你"},{"pid":"0b7357449684ec3da4c962bf369847b3a77a5688","tid":2023194,"uid":5094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T00:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}